'''热带风暴唐'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Don}}）是[[2011年大西洋飓风季|2011年大西洋飓风季]]第四场获得命名的风暴，也是该季首场[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。系统源于[[东风波|东风波]]沿线的[[低气压|低气压区]]，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机确认内部风速达到热带风暴强度后，系统于7月27日直接跳过热带低气压阶段升级成热带风暴。气旋经过[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]，并在达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时85公里的最高强度后减弱，再于7月30日以热带低气压标准登陆[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]。该州此时正遭受严重旱情，正期望风暴能产生足够降水，缓解灾情，但唐登陆后很快便已消散，对旱情影响甚微。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Don 2011 track.png}}
热带风暴唐源于7月16日位于非洲西岸近海的一股[[东风波|东风波]]<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Michael J. Brennan | date = 2011-10-28 | title = Tropical Storm Don Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194943/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL042011_Don.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL042011_Don.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] }}</ref>。接下来数天内，系统在大西洋开放海域上空向西移动，并带有少带局限在[[季风槽|季风槽]]中的[[对流|对流]]<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107170538.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-07-17 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | last = Wallace | first = Patricia | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083849/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107170538.txt }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107181746.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084025/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2011/TWDAT.201107181746.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-07-18 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | last1 = Formosa | first1 = Mike | last2 = Wallace | first2 = Patricia | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = TXT }}</ref>。7月21日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]首次在热带天气展望中预计位于[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]以东约1200公里的系统有潜力发展成热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107211758/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-07-21 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306134950/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107211758/index.php?basin=atl | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | last = Beven | first = Jack | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。7月23日，系统经过小安的列斯群岛，[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]出现热带风暴强度大风<ref name="tcr" />。受[[风切变|垂直风切变]]及附近陆地的共同影响，系统未能马上得以进一步发展<ref>{{cite report | last = Franklin | first = James | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306140337/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107232318/index.php?basin=atl | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107232318/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Weather Service | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-07-23 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | location = Miami, Florida }}</ref>。7月24日，东风波北部沿线的对流有所增长<ref name="tcr" />，但美国国家飓风中心次日预计系统不会出现显著发展<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107241132/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = [[美国国家气象局|National Weather Service]] | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-07-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141028144336/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201107241132/index.php?basin=atl | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | last = Pasch | first = Richard | archivedate = 2014-10-28 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

7月26日清晨，东风波沿线的[[雷暴|雷暴]]在古巴以南洋面上空聚拢，并同[[低气压|低气压区]]相连。系统继续组织，到了[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月27日早上6点，其表面环流已有显著改善，在行进至墨西哥[[坎昆|坎昆]]东北方向约95公里海域时成为热带低气压，并于不到12小时后增强成热带风暴。<ref name="tcr" />不过，美国国家飓风中心在当时的实际操作中直至{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}7月27日晚21点才在侦察机确认风暴内存在细长而封闭的环流中心后才把系统归类成热带气旋，并且直接跳过热带低气压阶段划分成热带风暴，以“唐”（{{lang|en|Don}}）为其命名。气旋形成后沿[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]北部上空的下到中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]的南部边缘朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动。由于外界环境渐趋有利，[[海面温度|水温]]较高，风切变只有轻到中度水平，气象机构预计唐会稳步增强，风速至少达到每小时100公里。但所有的[[热带气旋预测模型|热带气旋预测模型]]都认为风暴不会出现大幅强化。<ref name="d1">{{cite report | location = Miami, FL | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.001.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Don Discussion Number One | date = 2011-07-27 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Beven | first = Jack | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160329153104/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.001.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-29 }}</ref>

由于下层和中层环流没有对齐，唐起初未能显著增强<ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-04-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403132931/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.003.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Don Discussion Number Three | date = 2011-07-28 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | author1 = Blake | author2 = Brown | deadurl = no | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。7月28日，环流在风切变的影响下从对流中进一步暴露出来，但气旋风速却略有提高<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160402132356/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.004.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Don Discussion Number Four | date = 2011-07-28 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Beven | first = Jack | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-04-02 }}</ref>。7月29日清晨，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机确认风暴达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.006.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Don Discussion Number Six | date = 2011-07-29 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Avila | first = Lixion | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-04-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160401003253/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.006.shtml }}</ref>，并且穿越墨西哥湾期间强度得以保持<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Don Discussion Number Nine | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160402192401/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.009.shtml | date = 2011-07-29 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.009.shtml? | last = Beven | first = Jack | archivedate = 2016-04-02 | location = Miami, FL | deadurl = no }}</ref>。7月30日清晨，唐的对流在逼近德克萨斯州海岸期间因近海风切变增多，空气变得更加干燥，同时水温也更寒冷而迅速瓦解<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.010.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Don Discussion Number Ten | date = 2011-07-30 | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403130701/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.discus.010.shtml | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | last = Avila | first = Lixion | archivedate = 2016-04-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="bro">{{cite report | author = Brownsville, Texas National Weather Service | date = 2011-07-30 | title = Tropical Storm Don: Not Such a "Dandy" | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | publisher = National Weather Service | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034518/http://www.srh.noaa.gov/bro/?n=2011event_tropstormdon | deadurl = no | url = http://www.srh.noaa.gov/bro/?n=2011event_tropstormdon | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。对流消散同时，风暴的风速相应下滑，唐最终于{{lang|en|UTC}}7月30日凌晨2点30分以热带低气压强度从[[帕德里岛国家海岸|帕德里岛国家海岸]][[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]。登陆仅3个半小时后，唐就退化成残留低气压区，环流再坚持6小时后便完全消散。<ref name="tcr" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Tropical_storm_Don_(2011)_TRMM_image.jpg|right]]

[[金塔纳罗奥州|金塔纳罗奥州]][[民事防护|民防]]机构发出警报，称形成唐的东风波有可能在该州产生80到150毫米降水，持续风速可能达到每小时35到45公里，阵风时速65公里<ref>{{cite news | title = Onda tropical podría convertise en ciclón en Q.Roo | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/781901.html | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | newspaper = El Universal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141017061133/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/781901.html | date = 2011-07-27 | agency = Notimex | archivedate = 2014-10-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋成为热带风暴后，[[尤卡坦州|尤卡坦州]]政府宣布进入绿色警戒状态，这种级别的警戒表明唐虽然距离该州不远，但其威胁并不大<ref>{{cite news | title = Alerta verde por tormenta Don en Yucatán | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/782016.html | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305200517/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/782016.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2011-07-27 | agency = Notimex | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。7月27日晚，美国国家飓风中心向德克萨斯州[[威拉西县_(德克萨斯州)|威拉西县]][[曼斯菲尔德港_(德克萨斯州)|曼斯菲尔德港]]（{{lang|en|Port Mansfield}}）到[[加尔维斯顿岛|加尔维斯顿岛]][[圣路易斯海峡|圣路易斯海峡]]之间地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref>{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | title = Tropical Storm Don Advisory Number 2 | location = Miami, FL | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | date = 2011-07-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.public.002.shtml? | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-04-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160407085024/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.public.002.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>。6小时后，热带风暴观察预警的生效范围向南延伸至[[美墨边界|美墨边界]]<ref>{{cite report | last1 = Blake | first1 = Eric | last2 = Brown | first2 = Daniel | title = Tropical Storm Don Advisory Number 3 | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160413135813/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.public.003.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al04/al042011.public.003.shtml? | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-04-24 | date = 2011-07-28 | archivedate = 2016-04-13 }}</ref>。

风暴获命名后，德克萨斯州有关部门开始采取防灾措施。位于[[加尔维斯敦_(得克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]的[[得克萨斯大学系统|德克萨斯大学]][[德克萨斯大学医学分部|医学分部]]发布一级警告，政府著手準備可能用到的疏散計劃。<ref name="Reece">{{cite news | title = Galveston officials keeping an eye on Don | last = Reece | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120825102502/http://www.khou.com/news/Galveston-officials-keeping-an-eye-on-Don-126286208.html | url = http://www.khou.com/news/Galveston-officials-keeping-an-eye-on-Don-126286208.html | first = Kevin | date = 2011-07-27 | publisher = KHOU 11 | accessdate = 2013-12-26 | archivedate = 2012-08-25 }}</ref>7月27日，多家石油公司开始将墨西哥湾西部钻井平台上非必要的工作人员撤离<ref>{{cite news | last = Sullivan | first = Brian K. | title = Tropical Storm Don Forms Off Mexico’s Yucatan on Track for Texas Coast | archivedate = 2014-10-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141020081656/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/tropical-storm-don-forms-in-atlantic-ocean-on-track-to-southeastern-texas.html | newspaper = Bloomberg | date = 2011-07-27 | accessdate = 2014-10-20 | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/tropical-storm-don-forms-in-atlantic-ocean-on-track-to-southeastern-texas.html }}</ref>。次日，{{lang|en|[[BP|BP]]}}、[[荷兰皇家壳牌|荷兰皇家壳牌]]、[[阿纳达科石油公司|阿纳达科]]和[[阿帕奇公司|阿帕奇]]宣布会将墨西哥湾西部的部分石油设施撤离，[[艾克森美孚|艾克森美孚]]开始为[[贝敦炼油厂|贝敦炼油厂]]做好应对风暴来袭的准备<ref name="WSJ Oil shutin 07-28" />。截至7月28日中午，多家石油公司暂停石油开采，墨西哥湾内6.8%的原油和2.8%的天然气生产在气旋逼近前暂停<ref name="WSJ Oil shutin 07-28">{{cite news | last1 = Gonzalez | first1 = Angel | first2 = Isabel | last2 = Ordonez | first3 = Ryan | last3 = Dezember | title = 2nd UPDATE: Gulf Oil Producers Shut In Output Ahead Of Storm | newspaper = [[华尔街日报|Wall Street Journal]] | date = 2011-07-28}}</ref>。

唐在登陆前突然减弱，因此在德克萨斯州产生的降水很少，总量尚不足25毫米<ref name="bro" />。不过，位于登陆点东北方向很远的[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]][[湾城_(德克萨斯州)|湾城]]（{{lang|en|Bay City}}）却降下65毫米雨量<ref name="tcr" />。受降雨影响，德克萨斯州南部有部分道路失滑，湖泊水位升高<ref name="bro" />。降水令该州棉农受益，但对持续性的旱情影响有限<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = [[今日美国|USA Today]], Associated Press | date = 2011-07-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131021194331/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2011-07-30-tropical-storm-don-texas_n.htm | deadurl = no | title = Tropical system leaves little rain in dry Texas | accessdate = 2013-10-21 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2011-07-30-tropical-storm-don-texas_n.htm | archivedate = 2013-10-21 }}</ref>。气旋经过期间产生的风力很小，最强阵风时速为66公里。此外，唐登岸期间还产生0.58米高的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]，但没有任何报道表明风暴在该州造成破坏或人员伤亡。<ref name="tcr" />

